  " <C-C> seems to be essential here:
  "
   map    <buffer>  <silent>  <C-F9>        <C-C>:call Lua_Run()<CR>
  imap    <buffer>  <silent>  <C-F9>   <C-C><C-C>:call Lua_Run()<CR>
  "
